  <body>
    <noscript data-n-head="ssr" data-hid="gtm-noscript" data-pbody="true"><iframe src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/ns.html?id=G-49NFDD34M8&" height="0" width="0" style="display:none;visibility:hidden" title="gtm"></iframe></noscript><div data-server-rendered="true" id="__nuxt"><!----><div id="__layout"><div class="page page--home"><div role="dialog" class="gdpr"><div class="gdpr__content"><div class="small-text"><p>This website uses cookies to ensure you get the best experience.</p></div> <div class="gdpr__actions"><button type="button" class="primary-button">I Agree</button> <button type="button" class="primary-button">Set only essential cookies</button></div></div></div> <div class="home-hero"><div class="media"><div class="video-clip"><video loop muted playsinline poster="https://assets.thirdpoint.com/f/160155/1440x839/9dd9940d31/homehero.jpg/m/" aria-label="home hero" class="video-clip__video"><source data-src="https://assets.thirdpoint.com/f/160155/x/6f9a703676/tp-loop-30sec-20220427.mp4" type="video/mp4"></video></div></div> <div class="text"><img src="/img/ui/wordmark-small.svg" alt="Third Point" class="small"> <img src="/img/ui/wordmark-large.svg" alt="Third Point" class="large"></div></div> <header class="global-header"><a href="#content" id="skip-navigation">Skip Navigation</a> <nav class="global-nav"><a href="/" aria-current="page" class="global-logo active-exact active"><img src="/img/ui/logo.svg" alt="Third Point Logo"></a> <a href="/https://services.intralinks.com/logon/v3/index.html?clientID=7189174770" class="primary-button">Login </a> <button type="button" class="menu-button">Open Menu</button> <ul class="global-nav-list"><li><a href="/investment-strategy/" class="global-nav-list__link">Investment Strategy</a></li><li><a href="/giving-back/" class="global-nav-list__link">Giving Back</a></li><li><a href="/contact-us/" class="global-nav-list__link">Contact Us</a></li> <li><a href="https://services.intralinks.com/logon/v3/index.html?clientID=7189174770" class="primary-button">Login </a></li> <li><button aria-hidden="true"></button></li></ul></nav></header> <main id="content"><div class="text-block text-block--wide"><h1>Opportunistic investing in equities, corporate, structured, private credit, and CLO strategies, and venture capital.</h1></div><section class="tenets"><div class="tenets__intro"><h2 class="subtext"></h2> <!----></div> <div class="tenets__grid"><div class="tenets__item"><img src="https://assets.thirdpoint.com/f/160155/x/3f037d2e0a/icon-clock.svg" width="65" height="65" alt="Icon clock transparent background"> <div class="tenets__item__content"><p class="text-2">Decades</p> <p>of investing in public and private markets globally across the capital structure </p></div></div><div class="tenets__item"><img src="https://assets.thirdpoint.com/f/160155/x/ca96f8e872/icon-team.svg" width="65" height="65" alt="Team icon transparent background"> <div class="tenets__item__content"><p class="text-2">Opportunistic</p> <p>and engaged investors in long and short equities, corporate, structured, private, and CLO strategies, and venture capital</p></div></div><div class="tenets__item"><img src="https://assets.thirdpoint.com/f/160155/x/ca96f8e872/icon-team.svg" width="65" height="65" alt="Team icon transparent background"> <div class="tenets__item__content"><p class="text-2">Investors-first</p> <p>Ethos imbues all that we do </p></div></div><div class="tenets__item"><img src="https://assets.thirdpoint.com/f/160155/x/9f34cb649d/icon-kaizen.svg" width="65" height="65" alt="Kaizen icon with transparent background"> <div class="tenets__item__content"><p class="text-2">Expertise</p> <p>in investment sectors and strategies and the business functions needed to support them</p></div></div></div></section><blockquote class="blockquote blockquote--without-quotes"><p class="text-2">Third Point has acquired Birch Grove, a diversified credit asset manager, bringing CLO and other complimentary credit strategies to enhance offerings for our investors.</p> <footer><cite>  </cite></footer></blockquote><section class="leadership"><div class="leadership__intro"><div class="leadership__intro__text"><p class="subtext">Our Leadership</p> <h2>Meet the people behind Third Point</h2> <div><p class="ProseMirror__styled">Experienced professionals who embrace the principle that collaboration drives better results.</p></div></div> <div class="leadership__intro__nav"><button class="previous inactive"><span class="small"><svg width="34" height="19" viewBox="0 0 34 19" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><line x1="0" y1="9.5" x2="34" y2="9.5" style="stroke:#003b77;stroke-width:1"/><line x1="0" y1="9.5" x2="9.5" y2="0" style="stroke:#003b77;stroke-width:1"/><line x1="0" y1="9.5" x2="9.5" y2="19" style="stroke:#003b77;stroke-width:1"/></svg></span> <span class="large"><svg width="54" height="31" viewBox="0 0 54 31" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><line x1="0" y1="15.5" x2="54" y2="15.5" style="stroke:#003b77;stroke-width:1"/><line x1="0" y1="15.5" x2="15.5" y2="0" style="stroke:#003b77;stroke-width:1"/><line x1="0" y1="15.5" x2="15.5" y2="31" style="stroke:#003b77;stroke-width:1"/></svg></span></button> <button class="next inactive"><span class="small"><svg width="34" height="19" viewBox="0 0 34 19" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><line x1="0" y1="9.5" x2="34" y2="9.5" style="stroke:#003b77;stroke-width:1"/><line x1="34" y1="9.5" x2="24.5" y2="0" style="stroke:#003b77;stroke-width:1"/><line x1="34" y1="9.5" x2="24.5" y2="19" style="stroke:#003b77;stroke-width:1"/></svg></span> <span class="large"><svg width="54" height="31" viewBox="0 0 54 31" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><line x1="0" y1="15.5" x2="54" y2="15.5" style="stroke:#003b77;stroke-width:1"/><line x1="54" y1="15.5" x2="38.5" y2="0" style="stroke:#003b77;stroke-width:1"/><line x1="54" y1="15.5" x2="38.5" y2="31" style="stroke:#003b77;stroke-width:1"/></svg></span></button></div></div> <div class="leadership__people"><ul class="people"><li><div class="name"><h3>Daniel S. Loeb</h3> <p>Chief Executive Officer & Chief Investment Officer</p> <button></button></div> <div class="content"><div class="text"><p>Daniel S. Loeb is CEO of Third Point LLC, founded in 1995. Daniel has been at the front lines of investing in equities, credit and venture capital for his entire career.  He has served on numerous public company boards where he has driven substantial value to shareholders. Daniel graduated from Columbia University with an A.B. in economics, in 1983, endowed the Daniel S. Loeb Scholarship for undergraduate study there, and received the school’s John Jay Award for distinguished professional achievement. In October 2020, he was awarded the Alexander Hamilton Award for his philanthropic service by the Manhattan Institute.</p></div> <img src="https://assets.thirdpoint.com/f/160155/680x908/2ca478a5d7/daniel_loeb.jpg/m//340x450" alt="Daniel S. Loeb"></div></li><li><div class="name"><h3>Josh Targoff</h3> <p>President</p> <button></button></div> <div class="content"><div class="text"><p>Josh Targoff joined Third Point in 2008. Prior to joining Third Point, Mr. Targoff was the General Counsel of the Investment Banking Division of Jefferies & Co. Mr. Targoff spent seven years doing Mergers and Acquisitions transactional work at Debevoise & Plimpton LLP. Mr. Targoff graduated with a J.D. from Yale Law School and holds a B.A. from Brown University.</p></div> <img src="https://assets.thirdpoint.com/f/160155/680x908/78aeca0b78/josh_targoff.jpg/m//340x450" alt="Josh Targoff"></div></li><li><div class="name"><h3>Ian Wallace</h3> <p>Partner and Co-Head of Credit</p> <button></button></div> <div class="content"><div class="text"><p>Ian Wallace joined Third Point in 2009. Prior to joining Third Point, Mr. Wallace was the Managing Member of River Run Management, LLC, which he founded in 1999. River Run was a hedge fund focused on high yield and distressed investments and the firm shared office space with and partnered with Third Point on many successful distressed investments from 2000-2004. From 1989 to 1998, Mr. Wallace was a Managing Director with Oak Hill. Previously, Mr. Wallace was a Vice President in the High-Yield Research group at First Boston, and a staff accountant at Arthur Andersen & Co. Mr. Wallace graduated from the University of Washington with a B.A. in Business Administration.</p></div> <img src="https://assets.thirdpoint.com/f/160155/680x908/6795b032ba/ian_wallace.jpg/m//340x450" alt="Ian Wallace"></div></li><li><div class="name"><h3>Jonathan Berger</h3> <p>Co-Head of Credit and CEO/CIO of TP Birch Grove</p> <button></button></div> <div class="content"><div class="text"><p>Jonathan Berger is the Chief Executive Officer and Chief Investment Officer of TP Birch Grove and Co-Head of Credit of Third Point. In 2013, Jonathan co-founded Birch Grove Capital. Previously, he was the President and Chief Investment Officer of Stone Tower Capital, a $17 billion alternative credit asset management firm, where he was directly responsible for overseeing all investment activities, including $2 billion in credit hedge funds. Prior to that, Jonathan was a co-founder and partner of Pegasus Capital Advisors, a special situations private equity fund managing over $1.1 billion. He was responsible for developing and managing Pegasus’ investments in the public security markets and highly structured security investments. He also held prior roles as a Vice President in the High-Yield and Distressed Securities Group at UBS Securities; a Principal at Rosecliff, Inc., a middle-market private equity fund; and an Associate in the Leveraged Finance Group at Salomon Brothers Inc. Jonathan holds a BS in Economics with a concentration in Finance from the University of Pennsylvania’s Wharton School. He is a member of the Wharton Leadership Advisory Board of the University of Pennsylvania and serves as a Trustee on the Board of Race Against Dementia. </p></div> <img src="https://assets.thirdpoint.com/f/160155/1799x2015/44afaf66f0/berger_jonathan_35667_cropped.JPG/m//340x450" alt="Jonathan Berger"></div></li><li><div class="name"><h3>Shalini Sriram</h3> <p>Managing Director & Head of Structured Credit</p> <button></button></div> <div class="content"><div class="text"><p>Shalini Sriram is the Head of Structured Credit at Third Point and sits on the firm’s risk committee, overseeing a range of investments from residential and commercial mortgage backed securities to the intersection of consumer finance and technology. Prior to joining Third Point in 2017, Ms. Sriram invested in structured credit at Scoggin Capital. From 2006 to 2012, Ms. Sriram was an Executive Director at Morgan Stanley, and Head of ABS CDO and RMBS trading. From 2002 to 2006, Ms. Sriram was an associate at Bank of America Securities on a proprietary ABS trading desk where she first structured and then traded CDOs. Ms. Sriram received a B.A. in Economics cum laude in three years from Wellesley College and an MBA from Columbia Business School.</p></div> <img src="https://assets.thirdpoint.com/f/160155/680x908/833008891b/shalini.jpg/m//340x450" alt="Shalini Sriram"></div></li><li><div class="name"><h3>Rob Schwartz</h3> <p>Managing Partner, Third Point Ventures</p> <button></button></div> <div class="content"><div class="text"><p>Since June 2000, Mr. Schwartz has been Managing Partner of Third Point Ventures, the Menlo Park, California based venture capital arm of Third Point LLC, which is a registered investment adviser based in New York and the investment manager of the Third Point Funds. Mr. Schwartz is presently a director of NextSilicon, Sysdig, CipherTrace, Kentik, Kumu Networks, Aryaka, Upstart (Nasdaq:UPST), Precision Hawk, R2 Semiconductor, Rubicon Labs, SentinelOne, YellowBrick Data, Ushur, and Catalytic. Previously, for 23 years, Mr. Schwartz was the President of RF Associates North, a privately held communications semiconductor manufacturer’s representative firm. Mr. Schwartz holds a multi-discipline engineering degree from the University of California at Berkeley.</p></div> <img src="https://assets.thirdpoint.com/f/160155/680x908/70a18961a4/rob_s.jpg/m//340x450" alt="Rob Schwartz"></div></li><li><div class="name"><h3>Chris Taylor</h3> <p>Head of Private Credit</p> <button></button></div> <div class="content"><div class="text"><p>Chris Taylor is the Head of Private Credit.</p></div> <img src="https://assets.thirdpoint.com/f/160155/4192x2796/dcb8c14bec/chris-taylor.png/m//340x450" alt="Chris Taylor"></div></li></ul></div></section></main> <footer class="global-footer"><div class="global-footer__content"><div class="global-footer__logo"><a href="/" aria-current="page" class="active-exact active"><img src="/img/ui/logo-footer.svg" alt="Third Point Logo"></a></div> <div class="global-footer__info"><section class="global-footer-section"><h2 class="text-3">Contact Us</h2> <div><h4>To learn more about Birch Grove:</h4><p><a href="https://www.TPbirchgrove.com" target="_self" linktype="url">TP Birch Grove</a></p><p></p><h4>Investors:</h4><p><a href="mailto:ir@thirdpoint.com" linktype="url">ir@thirdpoint.com</a></p><p></p><h4>Applicants:</h4><p><a href="mailto:recruiting@thirdpoint.com" target="_blank" linktype="url">recruiting@thirdpoint.com</a></p><p></p><h4>Visit</h4><p>55 Hudson Yards<br>New York, NY 10001</p></div></section></div></div> <div class="global-footer__legal"><nav class="global-footer__legal__nav"><ul class="global-footer__list"><li><a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a></li><li><a href="/terms-of-use">Terms of Use</a></li><li><a href="/cookie-policy">Cookie Policy</a></li><li><a href="/gdpr-privacy-notice">Third Point Global Privacy Notice</a></li></ul></nav> <p>© 2023 Third Point LLC. All Rights Reserved.</p></div></footer> <div class="modal" style="display:none"><button type="button" class="modal__close-button">Close Modal</button> <!----> <button aria-hidden="true" class="modal__focus-trap-button"></button></div></div></div></div><script defer src="/_nuxt/static/1746131512/state.js"></script><script src="/_nuxt/13a078b.js" defer></script><script src="/_nuxt/54df313.js" defer></script><script src="/_nuxt/e43a52a.js" defer></script><script src="/_nuxt/9fbd15e.js" defer></script><script src="/_nuxt/8342dd1.js" defer></script><script src="/_nuxt/0e848ce.js" defer></script><script src="/_nuxt/03f37d4.js" defer></script>
